    ProfileEditorPage.resw (en-US) — all strings for the profile editor page.
    Static UI text uses x:Uid="/ProfileEditorPage/<Key>" in XAML (key "BasicHeader" -> data name "BasicHeader.Text").
    The code-generated rule-row UI (the BuildRuleRow family) and dialogs are fetched via Loc.T("ProfileEditorPage/<Key>");
    dynamic strings (e.g. "Rule N") use .NET composite-format indices ({0}) for Loc.T(key, args) -> string.Format.
    See docs/dev/I18N.md.
  -->
